---
---

<section class="about" id="about">
  <div class="about__inner">
    <h2 class="about__title">About us</h2>

    <div class="about__image-wrap">
      <img src="/img/about.jpg" alt="Industrial facility" class="about__image" loading="lazy" />
    </div>

    <p class="about__text">
      One Gate is a B2B sourcing and procurement gateway that helps
      businesses access supply from China with stronger control, greater
      efficiency, and higher commercial readiness. Built around the scale
      of the world's largest manufacturing hub, it offers a more
      structured path to cross-border sourcing.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    background: #FFFFFF;
    padding: 6rem 3.5rem;
  }

  .about__inner {
    max-width: 1440px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .about__title {
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 4.5vw, 4rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--forest);
    line-height: 1.05;
    letter-spacing: -0.015em;
  }

  .about__image-wrap {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .about__image {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 420px;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
  }

  .about__text {
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #3a3a3a;
    padding-top: 7rem;
    max-width: 380px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 960px) {
    .about { padding: 4rem 1.5rem; }
    .about__inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2rem; }
    .about__text { padding-top: 0; }
  }
</style>
